external_knowledge:
- "attracted the most attention" refers to the highest number of accesses;
- "papers" are documents or research articles uploaded by researchers;
- "accessed" means viewed or downloaded from a database or repository.

sql:
SELECT SUM(access_duration) AS total_access_duration
FROM access_logs
WHERE user_id = 1;

